Subject: [PATCH v7 11/20] dt-bindings: PCI: dwc: Add clocks/resets common properties
Date:   Sun, 13 Nov 2022 22:12:52 +0300
Message-ID: <20221113191301.5526-12-Sergey.Semin@baikalelectronics.ru>
